<h4>
  Floodplain Charts
  <button class="button tiny no-margin {{if (not-eq mode '2015') 'hollow'}}" style="border-top-right-radius: 0; border-bottom-right-radius:0" {{action "setMode" "2015"}}>2015 Floodplain</button><button class="button tiny no-margin {{if (not-eq mode '2050s') 'hollow'}}" style="border-top-left-radius: 0; border-bottom-left-radius:0" {{action "setMode" "2050s"}}>2050s Floodplain</button>
</h4>

<div class="grid-x grid-padding-x">
  <div class="cell medium-6 large-6 xlarge-5">
    <h4 class="subsection-header"><strong>Buildings in Floodplain {{info-tooltip tip="Counts of buildings on lots that lie within the 2015 PFIRM"}}</strong></h4>
    <div class="callout text-center">
      {{#building-type-chart property='numbldgs' floodplainSQL=floodplainSQL borocd=model.borocd as |chart|}}
        <p>
          <span class="stat">
            {{numeral-format (reduce (action 'sum') 0 (map-by 'value' (await chart.data))) '0,0'}}
          </span>
          <span class="stat-footer">buildings are in the current floodplain</span>
        </p>
      {{/building-type-chart}}
      <hr>
      <span class="chart-legend">
        <span class="nobreak"><span class="total"></span> Total Buildings</span>
        &nbsp;
        <span class="nobreak"><span class="percent"></span> Within Floodplain</span>
      </span>
      {{resiliency-chart
          column='cd_tot_bldgs'
          overlayColumn='current_fp_bldg'
          numeral_format='0,0'
          borocd=model.borocd}}
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cell medium-6 large-6 xlarge-5">
    <h4 class="subsection-header"><strong>Dwelling Units in Floodplain {{info-tooltip tip="Counts of residential units on lots that lie within the 2015 PFIRM"}}</strong></h4>
    <div class="callout text-center">
      {{#building-type-chart property='unitsres' floodplainSQL=floodplainSQL borocd=model.borocd as |chart|}}
        <p>
          <span class="stat">
              {{numeral-format (reduce (action 'sum') 0 (map-by 'value' (await chart.data))) '0,0'}}
          </span>
          <span class="stat-footer">dwelling units are in the current floodplain</span>
        </p>
      {{/building-type-chart}}
      <hr>
      <span class="chart-legend">
        <span class="nobreak"><span class="total"></span>&nbsp;Total Units</span>
        &nbsp;
        <span class="nobreak"><span class="percent"></span>&nbsp;Within Floodplain</span>
      </span>
      {{resiliency-chart
          column='cd_tot_resunits'
          overlayColumn='current_fp_resunits'
          numeral_format='0,0'
          borocd=model.borocd
          unit='units'}}
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cell medium-6 xlarge-4">
    <h4 class="subsection-header"><strong>Age of Buildings in Floodplain {{info-tooltip tip="Counts of buildings on lots that lie within the 2015 PFIRM"}}</strong></h4>
    <div class="callout">
      <p class="text-small">These counts are grouped based on {{#link-to 'about' (query-params section='floodplain')}}important dates{{/link-to}} in the history of NYCâ€™s land-use and floodplain regulation.</p>
      {{building-age-chart borocd=model.borocd floodplainSQL=floodplainSQL}}
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cell medium-6 xlarge-4">
    <h4 class="subsection-header"><strong>Basements in Floodplain {{info-tooltip tip="Counts of buildings with basements that lie within the 2015 PFIRM"}}</strong></h4>
    <div class="callout">
      <p class="text-small">Basements are highly vulnerable to flooding and can lead to higher retrofitting costs.</p>
      {{subgrade-chart borocd=model.borocd floodplainSQL=floodplainSQL}}
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cell medium-6 xlarge-4">
    <h4 class="subsection-header"><strong>Residential Buildings by Adjacency {{info-tooltip tip="Counts of adjacent buildings that lie within the 2015 PFIRM"}}</strong></h4>
    <div class="callout">
      <p class="text-small">Buildings that are fully or partially attached are harder to elevate or retrofit to minimize flood risk.</p>
      {{adjacency-chart borocd=model.borocd floodplainSQL=floodplainSQL}}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{{yield}}
